{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"certifiable":true,"findings":[{"citations":[{"description":"Ticket status: in_progress; ticket has a plan-review PASS signature but no completion-verifier signature and no Gerrit landing evidence recorded.","kind":"source"}],"criterion":"`make lint && make typecheck && make test` green; landed through Gerrit.","detail":"This criterion requires both that the CI suite passes and that the change has been landed through Gerrit. The ticket status is 'in_progress' (not closed/merged), and there is no attestation or commit evidence in the repository that the change has been landed through Gerrit or that `make lint && make typecheck && make test` are green. No tagged [operator-attested] evidence (specific Gerrit change id, merge commit, CI run URL) was recorded on the ticket.","dimension":"completion","remediation":"Record proof as a ticket comment naming the Gerrit change URL/id, the observed CI outcome (lint/typecheck/test green), and the merge timestamp. Alternatively, tag this criterion [operator-attested] and provide that concrete attestation.","reviewer_id":"completion-verifier","severity":"high"}],"material_fingerprint":null,"model":"anthropic:claude-sonnet-4-6","remediation":"How to resolve the unmet criteria: for each one, decide whether the work is genuinely incomplete or simply undocumented. If a requirement is already satisfied but the proof is not discoverable from the code alone, add a comment to this ticket that documents the evidence — cite the concrete artifacts that meet the requirement (file paths and line ranges, commands and their output, links, or the reasoning that ties the work to the criterion). The completion verifier reads this ticket's comments, so evidence you record there is taken into account on the next verification. For any criterion whose work is genuinely unfinished, complete it, then re-verify.","runner":"pydantic_ai","schema":"completion_verifier_fail_v1","ticket_id":"b1a4-af7a-4a48-465d","verdict":"FAIL"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMPLETION_VERDICT","timestamp":1784315707468479001,"uuid":"d367c373-6b40-4301-8cec-9c66ab9d1aaa"}